BEY
v.
RASAWEHR 2019-0295 Supreme Court of Ohio. March 13, 2019

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULING

On motion for admission pro hac vice of Eugene Volokh. Motion granted. Pursuant to Gov.Bar R. XII(4), counsel shall file a notice of permission to appear pro hac vice with the Supreme Court's Office of Attorney Services within 30 days.
